<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 05 at 6:34PM EST  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...Locally Dense Fog...
Fog has developed across portions of the mid-Hudson Valley and
northwestern Connecticut with some locally dense resulting in
visibilities of less than a half of a mile at times. Motorists are
urged to allow for extra time to get to their destination and
leave plenty of space between vehicles. Conditions are expected to
improve later this evening.</description>
